SOCCER - INJURED N ' GOTTY OUT FOR UP TO A MONTH . French international midfielder Bruno N ' Gotty , injured during Paris St Germain ' s 3 - 0 victory over FC Vaduz in a European Cupwinners Cup match last week , will be out of action for up to a month , PSG doctors said on Tuesday . N ' Gotty , 25 , has a torn right calf muscle and will miss PSG ' s league match in Lyon on Wednesday . He is also forced out of the French squad for a friendly international between France and Turkey next week in Paris . The injury came as blow both for PSG and France as their goalkeeper Bernard Lama is also out through injury . PSG also rested Leonardo from training on Tuesday . The Brazilian was hurt in a league match at Guingamp on Sunday but the seriousness of the injury is not yet known . 
